text: Jay Pande (20 September 1994) is an Indian cricketer who plays for Maharashtra. He made his List A debut for Maharashtra against Goa in the 2018-19 Vijay Hazare Trophy on 19 September 2018. He made his first-class debut for Maharashtra in the 2018–19 Ranji Trophy on 28 November 2018. == References == == External links== * Jay Pande at ESPN Cricinfo Category:1994 births Category:Cricketers from Pune Category:Indian cricketers Category:Living people
